## Problem Statement: Sorted Student names##


A class contains a static method sortStudents(..) which takes two arrays of same size.
The First array is a String array containing the names of Students.The second array is an integer array containing the percentage obtained by the students in their exams. 

The method returns a String array with Students name, sorted as per the ascending order of their percentages

Please complete the method to achieve the functionality given above.


Write a main method and accept input from console as per the format below

Sample Input:

Rahul:75;Girish:65;John:80;


This data has to be passed to the method sortStudents(..) and the returned array should be printed as below

Sample Output:

[Girish, Rahul, John]

